OL,3,CStarmer's Mandelson misjudgment laid
OL,4,Cbare
OL,6,FAnd significant detail about
OL,7,FMandelson's "particularly close
OL,8,Frelationship" - quoting mega bank JP
OL,9,FMorgan - with the convicted paedophile
OL,10,FJeffrey Epstein.
OL,12,FIt spells out that their relationship
OL,13,Fcontinued "across 2009-11," after
OL,14,FEpstein was imprisoned for procuring a
OL,15,Fchild for prostitution, and while
OL,16,FMandelson was business secretary in
OL,17,FGordon Brown's government.
OL,26,@oD@MOUpD@MO]uD@KOUuD@[O]
