PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773259872
OL,3,CStarmer's Mandelson misjudgment laid
OL,4,Cbare
OL,6,FMaybe one day that will be clearer,
OL,7,Fwhen the Met Police allow the
OL,8,Fpublication of Mandelson's answers to
OL,9,Fthree questions put to him about his
OL,10,Ffriendship with Epstein by Starmer's
OL,11,Fthen chief of staff Morgan McSweeney -
OL,12,Fwho was championing Mandelson's
OL,13,Fappointment to one of the most
OL,14,Fimportant and sensitive jobs in
OL,15,Fgovernment.
OL,17,FBut it is difficult to imagine what
OL,18,FMandelson could possibly have said in
OL,19,Freply that would today be seen as
OL,20,Fredeeming Starmer from his terrible
OL,21,Fmisjudgment in choosing him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
